{
    "name": "Stonefish Swarm",
    "type": "creature",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Stonefish Swarm",
            "type": "section",
            "text": "Stonefish occasionally band together where food is abundant, filling all nooks and crannies of a coral reef. In large numbers, stonefish can take on prey much larger than themselves.",
